<br>
I am a 61 Mage planning my AA options - The Class AA Quick Summon in the few places I have investigated mentions QS effects &quot;all&quot; conjuration spells - I am more inclined to believe this is all pet summon spells - is this the case or does it really mean &quot;all&quot; conjuration spells?<br>
<br>
Mazia<br>
<br>
ps. My route presently is basically:<br>
<br>
3   3 to Running<br>
6   3 to Regeneration<br>
<br>
8   2 to Spell casting Mastery<br>
12  4 to Spell casting Mastery<br>
18  6 to Spell casting Mastery<br>
<br>
23  at 62 5 Suspend Minion<br>
28  at 63 5 Host of the elements<br>
31  at 64 3 Suspend Minion<br>
36  at 64 5 Host of the elements<br>
41  at 65 5 host of the elements<br>
<br>
possibly looking to stick QS in there somewhere<br>
<br>
 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showUserPublicProfile?gid=falkahnhan>Falkahnhan</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_bluespot.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Magician</span><br>  Posts: 36<br> <font color=#333333>(1/16/03 10:19:10 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm30.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=512.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://home.earthlink.net/~nanosphere/hosicon_flag.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Quick Summoning Noob Question</span><hr size=1> QS only effect the pet summoning spells, it'd rock if it were all conjuration based spells though.<br>
<br>
<br>
Falkahnhan <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showUserPublicProfile?gid=cydmab>Cydmab</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Sage</span><br>  Posts: 726<br> <font color=#333333>(1/16/03 10:21:24 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm30.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=512.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Quick Summoning Noob Question</span><hr size=1> pets AND SUMMONED ITEMS and Call of the hero. Like mod rods, coldstones, etc. Does not effect heals, buffs, nukes, etc.<br>
<br>
