<br>
Go to level 62 (water pet)<br>
Get run 3, regen 3, SCM 3, pet hold, MC1<br>
Go to level 64 (may speed up leveling if you find some level 63/64 spells)<br>
Get suspend minion 1+2<br>
Get QS1<br>
Get HoE<br>
Get SCF 3; PoP SCF 1<br>
<br>
That will keep you busy for awhile. <p>Master Cydmab Promethean<br>
