<br>
QS2 is 25% and the ring is 15%<br>
<br>
Still, definitely not worth 9 aa points just to get another 10% speed on summoning... <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showUserPublicProfile?gid=zyphyr>Zyphyr</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Sage</span><br>  Posts: 809<br> <font color=#333333>(1/21/03 11:04:35 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm30.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=512.topic&index=7>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Quick Summoning Noob Question</span><hr size=1> Ylaine said &quot;Summoning Haste&quot; which is 25%, not &quot;Spell Haste&quot; which is 15%.<br>
<br>
