<br>
However, I <!--EZCODE UNDERLINE START--><span style="text-decoration:underline">really</span><!--EZCODE UNDERLINE END--> notice the difference between six second pets and five second pets.  One second does not seem like much, but when chaining or coping with adds, it makes a noticeable difference.  Also, I have no level 4 focus items, not even the summoned ones yet, but the AA's apply to spells of all levels.<br>
<br>
Five second pets, and you will feel a lot less vulnerable as a mage.<br>
